Every time something needs to be random inside a life, it should be seeded random so that the lives can be fully reproducible.

Every feature needs to include a logging system. the logs are displayed to the user and classified by type of log.

the architecture should allow as much as possible for mods. any content like repositories should be stored in json files that allow for easy modification and expansion.
